result.name: Super Super Congee & Noodles

reviews.text: Won ton noodle is the signature item. Must try. Excellent quality in such a fast food type shop, compared favourably to other so called won ton noodle specialty shops. Other items are only slightly above average.
Fast food restaurant for congee and Chinese noodle.

The highest quality fast food chain in Hong Kong but price point is a little higher than other big fast food chains. Can get very crowded at peak times. 
You can get all sorts of popular hk style dishes such as wonton noodles, fishball noodles, congee, hotpot for one, clay pot rice etc. 
Breakfasts are lovely too they have both Chinese style and western style breakfast set. Biggest downside is the smaller network of outlets and there isn’t an outlet where I live and where I work:(.
Compare with others brand name fast food places, this one is so clean.  And the quality of foods are very good.  The prices are so reasonable.  Worth to go many times.
Bought a congee with meat & corn, it tasted sour.
